{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/workflowui\/uikit\/uiviewcontroller\/environment"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"environment","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV","text":"ViewEnvironment","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/ViewEnvironment"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to provide overrides for the environment as it flows through a node, you should conform to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"type":"text","text":" and provide those overrides in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customize(environment:)"},{"type":"text","text":". E.g.:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["func customize(environment: inout ViewEnvironment) {","    environment.traits.mode = .dark","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, this property gets the environment by recursively walking to the root of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation path, and applying customizations on the way back down. The invalidation path may be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interrupted if a node has set it’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentAncestor"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", even if there is a node"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which specifies this node as an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentDescendant"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you’d like to update the return value of this variable and have those changes propagated through the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"propagation hierarchy, conform to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"text":" and call ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setNeedsEnvironmentUpdate()"},{"text":" and wait","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"for the system to call ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"apply(context:)"},{"text":" when appropriate (e.g. on the next layout pass for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"text":"\/","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"text":" subclasses).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Important","style":"important","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"type":"text","text":" conformers "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"must","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"applyEnvironmentIfNeeded()"},{"type":"text","text":" in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"viewWillLayoutSubviews()"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"layoutSubviews()"},{"type":"text","text":" respectively."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironment"},{"type":"text","text":" that is flowing through the propagation hierarchy."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI","doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/UIKit","doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/UIKit\/UIViewController"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/UIKit\/UIViewController\/environ